拒绝 996，生活和工作同样重要。”，“坚决抵制 996 工作制，维护社会健康和谐发展。举报监督电话：9962965”。这样做是不是会减少 996 的公司。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/745439","replies":82,"created_ts":1610767271,"created":"11:21:11","title":"996 工作是不是类似于地铁上的乞讨","author":"taogen","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/taogen","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5f16eccf4fb12baac91df365bf33a3d4?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":745432,"node":"互联网","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/internet","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9f61/408e/56_mini.png?m=1609151689","description":"<p>还有人说通过短视频学到不少东西，这智商得有多低才通过短视频学习</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/745432","replies":78,"created_ts":1610766272,"created":"11:04:32","title":"短视频真的越来越垃圾，我看得越多，自己变得越垃圾","author":"henryhu","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/henryhu","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5cba/6e74/12584_mini.png?m=1574602478"},{"id":745451,"node":"分享创造","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/create","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1596015931","description":"<p><a href=\"https://jarenchow.github.io/JanvasExamples/html/coderain.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">演示地址</a>\n<a href=\"https://codepen.io/jarenchow/pen/rNMQpMe\" rel=\"nofollow\">CodePen</a>\n此示例可以轻易自定义各种参数，或者嵌入自己的网站。</p>\n<p>虽然我现在做前端 Web 开发，但是做页面或业务还是及不上自己创造的感觉，所以在一段努力之后创造了基于 HTML5 Canvas 2d 的开发框架 <a href=\"https://github.com/jarenchow/janvas\" rel=\"nofollow\">janvas</a>。</p>\n<p>在此基础上开发了一些示例的代码：<a href=\"https://github.com/jarenchow/janvasexamples\" rel=\"nofollow\">janvasexamples</a></p>\n<p>目前在考虑想接需求，或者大家有推荐的好点的做内容输出的网站吗，比如 CSDN 一类的。</p>\n<p>顺便可不可以求一点小心心。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/745451","replies":66,"created_ts":1610770400,"created":"12:13:20","title":"几乎 100% 还原了黑客帝国中的代码雨特效","author":"M3oM3oBug","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/M3oM3oBug","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/43c3/62b9/160471_mini.png?m=1492786119"},{"id":745534,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/